title: Garden Weeding machine
body:
ITEM#: 41407774
Total length 43.7, yellow and black. This is the perfect choice for weeding tools, especially for main root plants, with durable and high-strength materials, comfortable and soft large plastic handles.

The protrusion on the grip can reduce slipping, especially when the hand is sweating. Protect your back and knees with a length of 43.7 inches. Release hands by pressing decay and buttons to remove weeds from tools. Control weeds, free from harmful chemicals, and safe for children, pets, and the environment.

Use this lawn mower outdoors, in gardens or backyard. Make your time in the garden more interesting and enjoyable.
